  <prompt>
    The `/project-pipeline` constrained run (2026-06-10) performed a plan-time pre-flight investigation per FR-03 and applied the finding to spec.md. This task ratifies the finding with implementation-level confirmation: read every claim in spec.md FR-03 + Resolution Decisions row "FR-03", verify against the named files, and produce `notes/insight-component-reuse-investigation.md` + `decisions/DR-001-component-reuse.md`. If the plan-time finding is wrong on any point, file the divergence in DR-001 with empirical evidence and surface to owner before Task 010.
  </prompt>

  <role>UI architect with Spaarke Fluent v9 + AI-widget package experience.</role>

  <goal>
    Two deliverables: `notes/insight-component-reuse-investigation.md` (raw findings + file paths) + `decisions/DR-001-component-reuse.md` (ratified decision). Confirm: `InsightSummaryCard` ships in `@spaarke/ai-widgets`; uses Fluent v9 Popover + Dialog composition (no extant inline-expand-to-modal pattern); reuses `AiSummaryPopover` lazy-load + state-machine shape; does NOT use `FeedbackButtons` (Q-U3 deferred).
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="spec">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/spec.md (FR-03 + Resolution Decisions)</file>
    <file purpose="plan">projects/ai-spaarke-insights-engine-widgets-r1/plan.md (Phase 0 Task 001)</file>
