  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="Read AiSummaryPopover.tsx">Document the state machine, props, lazy-load callback, Sparkle icon import</step>
    <step order="2" name="Inventory @spaarke/ai-widgets package">List exports, verify v0.1.0, identify build/lint/Storybook readiness</step>
    <step order="3" name="Search for any other inline-expand-to-modal pattern">grep `Dialog.*Popover`, `expand-to-modal`, `Modal.*inline` across `src/client/shared/`</step>
    <step order="4" name="Author notes/insight-component-reuse-investigation.md">Record: package home decision, AiSummaryPopover reuse points, gaps (no full modal expand), proposed composition approach</step>
    <step order="5" name="Author decisions/DR-001-component-reuse.md">Ratify (or contradict) the plan-time finding; cite evidence; one decision; one rationale</step>
